title: Genesis Lacy
text:
Hello! My name is Genesis Lacy and I’m currently a 4th year student at Colorado State University studying ecosystem science and sustainability.
Experience from my classes
ArcGIS Pro | Field work and data analysis | Working with local stakeholders
This website was made using Quarto. To learn more about Quarto websites visit https://quarto.org/docs/websites.

title: Projects
text:
Things that I learned with this project:

Indentations in code are important!
I’ve become more confident about where to find and create quarto documents and htmls.
To learn how to be patient with myself and giving myself time to learn something entirely new to me.
In the future I’m planning on:

Working on adding a better theme that will include more colors
Editing my pg footer so that it looks nicer
